member.param:
The attendance data to record, provided in the request body as an object.
Example Request:
POST /Attendance/TakeAttendance { "timeOfAttend": "2025-03-24T08:30:00Z", "latitude": 40.7128, "longitude": -74.0060, "employeeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000", "branch": "Main branch" }

member.response:
Successfully recorded the attendance. Returns the employee ID and a confirmation message.
Example Response:

{
    "employeeId": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
    "message": "Attendance added successfully."
}

